column2: SELECT TOP # FLOOR(petroMag_r-#*log1#(dbo.fCosmoDl(s.z))#-extinction_r) as M, COUNT(*) as count FROM SpecObj s INNER JOIN PhotoObj ON s.bestObjID=PhotoObj.ObjID WHERE s.z BETWEEN # AND #    AND objTypeName = &&& GROUP BY FLOOR(petroMag_r-#*log1#(dbo.fCosmoDl(s.z))#-extinction_r) ORDER BY #
